    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/302a4/chatbot.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/09011/chatbot.avif 225w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/e46ac/chatbot.avif 450w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/9b8d4/chatbot.avif 900w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/d8ca6/chatbot.avif 1080w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/d7e55/chatbot.webp 225w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/8626f/chatbot.webp 450w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/131f1/chatbot.webp 900w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/260c2/chatbot.webp 1080w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/3684f/chatbot.png 225w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/fc2a6/chatbot.png 450w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/1cfc2/chatbot.png 900w,\n/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/302a4/chatbot.png 1080w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/20aeb58c0277b311ee65af4103d2e1bc/1cfc2/chatbot.png\"\n            alt=\"Our Chatbot Solution\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Our Chatbot Solution</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>We reduced customer communication time and make life easier for customers</p>\n<p>ü§ñ A Chatbot for Communicating with the Codecave Team ü§ñ</p>\n<p>We have our own chatbot that redirects all messages sent to it to the team chat.</p>\n<p>Why is it Convenient?\nOur manager, whose contact information is listed on the website, may be unavailable for various reasons (vacation, sick leave, or high workload). However, our clients can receive timely answers and save waiting time by redirecting their questions to the general team chat.</p>\n<p>Competence of the Interlocutor</p>\n<p>Customers may have questions on various topics. Some might want to discuss business processes, while others might want to talk about development processes. In this case, our clients don't need to search for someone who \"knows\" the topic of their question. They can simply write to the bot and receive a prompt response.\nYou can find a link to the bot on our website in the ‚ÄúContacts‚Äù section.</p>\n<p>üíµ Our accounting Chatbot</p>\n<p>When working with accounting, our team used to manually create tasks in Microsoft Planner and transfer the related documentation from the chatbot to Telegram. With the advent of the chatbot, we can now spend more time solving tasks rather than creating them. Simply bookmarking a message ensures that all subsequent documents are entered into the new task.\nAdditionally, our bot has several commands for managing tasks. With these commands, you can:</p>\n<p>üè∑Ô∏è Get a list of tasks that have not been started.\nüè∑Ô∏è Start a task by replying to the message from which the task was created and writing ‚Äústart‚Äù.\nüè∑Ô∏è Finalize a task by replying with ‚Äúclose‚Äù.\nüè∑Ô∏è Return a completed task with the command ‚Äúreturn‚Äù.</p>\n<p><strong>We wish you a great mood and interesting tasks!</strong></p>","wordCount":{"words":293}},"author":{"frontmatter":{"authorAlias":"Zakruzhnaya","author":"Olga Zakruzhnaya","authorPosition":"Marketing specialist","authorPhoto":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/d4a57/author.jpg","srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/40657/author.jpg 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/77b35/author.jpg 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/d4a57/author.jpg 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/19e71/author.jpg 128w","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/e8e20/author.avif 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/b6d61/author.avif 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/2e71d/author.avif 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/3c49f/author.avif 128w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/e789a/author.webp 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/ef6ff/author.webp 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/8257c/author.webp 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/6766a/author.webp 128w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"}]},"width":64,"height":64}}}}}},"pageContext":{"id":"d7e62388-473f-5dcb-9a9b-90c64e9122ee","lang":"en","markupData":{"bannerTitle":"Well unknown facts","blogByAuthorBannerTitle":"Articles by the author","blogByHashtagBannerTitle":"Articles Featuring","head":"CodeCave Insights","readPostLink":"Open article","readingTimeTitle":"read","readingTimeUnits":"min","postFooterTitle":"Congratulations! Now you can show off with your new knowledge!","postFooterText":"